# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
debug/
target/

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# RustRover
#  JetBrains specific template is maintained in a separate JetBrains.gitignore that can
#  be found at https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/JetBrains.gitignore
#  and can be added to the global gitignore or merged into this file.  For a more nuclear
#  option (not recommended) you can uncomment the following to ignore the entire idea folder.
#.idea/

**/.DS_Store
**/node_modules

engine/dist

private.md

backup

# Solana test validator ledger (local dev only)
test-ledger/
**/test-ledger/
.anchor/test-ledger/

# ── Decoupled from the desktop client build ───────────────────────────────────
# The Solana contract (chain/) and the legacy chain-coupled frontend (app/) are
# no longer part of the standalone 3D engine + desktop client (client/desktop/).
# See docs/plan/STANDALONE_ENGINE_ROADMAP.md.
# app/ and chain/ were untracked via `git rm -r --cached app chain` (commit f669ea1)
# and remain on disk as a parked local archive (chain/docs/, chain/deploy/ live here too).
/app/
/chain/

# Client build artifacts (PWA frontends under client/)
client/*/dist/
client/*/dev-dist/

# Playwright (e2e) artifacts
**/test-results/
client/*/playwright-report/
client/*/e2e/__screenshots__/
**/.last-run.json
deploy/logs/

client/*/dist-chain/
services/*/data/
